                With 12,000 watts of floor shaking digital surround sound, you’ll feel like you’re there.
                Whether it’s hang-gliding through the majestic Grand Canyon in Vistor Center, AZ,
                shooting the mighty Colorado River rapids, scaling the top of Mount Everest or speeding
